An Unreasonable Man;;87;;92;;NC;;Filmmakers Henriette Mantel and Steve Krovan examine the notable career of activist and consumer advocate Ralph Nader. Using a blend of archival film footage and interviews, they chronicle his many accomplishments as well as his controversial bids for the presidency in 1996, 2000 and 2004.;;Documentary;;Henriette Mantel,Steve Skrovan;;2006;;NC;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/unreasonable_man